title: Garage Door Template Cover
content:
- platform: template
  covers:
    double_garage_door:
      device_class: garage
      friendly_name: "Double Garage Door"
      unique_id: doublegaragedoor
      value_template: "{{ is_state('binary_sensor.shellyplus2pm_80646fdb8b20_input_0', 'off') }}"
      availability_template: "{{ states('binary_sensor.shellyplus2pm_80646fdb8b20_input_0') in ['on','off'] }}"
      open_cover:
        - condition: state
          entity_id: binary_sensor.shellyplus2pm_80646fdb8b20_input_0
          state: "on"
        - action: switch.turn_on
          target: { entity_id: switch.double_garage_door }
      close_cover:
        - condition: state
          entity_id: binary_sensor.shellyplus2pm_80646fdb8b20_input_0
          state: "off"
        - action: switch.turn_on
          target: { entity_id: switch.double_garage_door }
      stop_cover:
        - action: switch.turn_on
          target: { entity_id: switch.double_garage_door }

-- ============================================================================
-- MEKANISM AUTOMATION SYSTEM
-- ============================================================================
-- Script para automaÃ§Ã£o completa de processamento de recursos usando Mekanism
-- Executa a cada 20 ticks (1 segundo) para manter eficiÃªncia
-- Autor: Thiago Oliveira Cabral ( github.com/Larbaco/ )
-- VersÃ£o: 1.0
-- ============================================================================

name "Mekanism Automation"
every 20 ticks do
    
    -- ========================================================================
    -- DISTRIBUIÃ‡ÃƒO DE ENERGIA (FORGE ENERGY - FE)
    -- ========================================================================
    -- Distribui energia da bateria principal para todas as mÃ¡quinas do sistema
    
    -- Alimenta mÃ¡quinas principais (lado sul)
    input fe:: from battery_supply
    output fe:: to machines south side

    -- Alimenta buffer de energia secundÃ¡rio
    input fe:: from battery_supply
    output fe:: to fe_buffer

    -- ========================================================================
    -- SISTEMA DE INFUSORES METALÃšRGICOS - CONTROLE DE QUÃMICOS
    -- ========================================================================
    -- MantÃ©m nÃ­veis mÃ­nimos de produtos quÃ­micos nos infusores
    -- Prioriza o sistema de armazenamento principal
    
    -- Infusor de Redstone (Redstone Enriquecida)
    if metallurgic_infuser_redstone has lt 10 redstone then
        input 10 enriched_redstone from system_storage
        output enriched_redstone to metallurgic_infuser_redstone top side
    end
    forget 

    -- Infusor de Carbono (Carbono Enriquecido)
    if metallurgic_infuser_carbon has lt 10 carbon then
        input 10 enriched_carbon from system_storage
        output enriched_carbon to metallurgic_infuser_carbon top side
    end
    forget 

    -- Infusor de Diamante (Diamante Enriquecido)
    if metallurgic_infuser_diamond has lt 10 diamond then
        input 10 enriched_diamond from system_storage
        output enriched_diamond to metallurgic_infuser_diamond top side
    end
    forget

    -- Infusor de Obsidiana (Obsidiana Refinada Enriquecida)
    if metallurgic_infuser_obsidian has lt 10 refined_obsidian then
        input 10 enriched_refined_obsidian from system_storage
        output enriched_refined_obsidian to metallurgic_infuser_obsidian top side
    end
    forget

    -- Compressor de Ã“smio (Lingote de Ã“smio)
    if osmium_compressor has lt 10 osmium then
        input 10 osmium_ingot from system_storage
        output osmium_ingot to osmium_compressor top side
    end

    -- ========================================================================
    -- SISTEMA DE FORNALHAS
    -- ========================================================================
    -- Alimenta fornalhas com materiais do chest de entrada
    
    input from input_smelter
    output to smelter east side
    forget

    -- ========================================================================
    -- COLETA DE PRODUTOS PROCESSADOS
    -- ========================================================================
    -- Coleta todos os produtos finalizados das mÃ¡quinas (lado leste)
    -- Envia automaticamente para o armazenamento principal
    
    input from machines east side
    output to system_storage

    -- ========================================================================
    -- ALIMENTAÃ‡ÃƒO DOS INFUSORES METALÃšRGICOS
    -- ========================================================================
    -- Processa materiais brutos dos chests de entrada especÃ­ficos
    
    -- Infusor de Redstone - materiais brutos (lado leste)
    input from input_mi_redstone
    output to metallurgic_infuser_redstone east side
    forget

    -- Infusor de Carbono - materiais brutos (lado leste)
    input from input_mi_carbon
    output to metallurgic_infuser_carbon east side
    forget 

    -- Infusor de Diamante - materiais brutos (lado leste)
    input from input_mi_diamond
    output to metallurgic_infuser_diamond east side
    forget

    -- Infusor de Obsidiana - materiais brutos (lado leste)
    input from input_mi_obsidian
    output to metallurgic_infuser_obsidian east side
    forget

    -- ========================================================================
    -- FÃBRICA DE ENRIQUECIMENTO
    -- ========================================================================
    -- Processa minerais para versÃµes enriquecidas
    
    input from input_ef
    output to enrichment_factory east side
    forget

    -- ========================================================================
    -- SERRA DE PRECISÃƒO
    -- ========================================================================
    -- Processa madeira e materiais similares
    
    input from input_ps
    output to precision_sawmill east side
    forget

    -- ========================================================================
    -- TRITURADOR
    -- ========================================================================
    -- Processa minerais brutos em pÃ³/fragmentos
    
    input from input_crusher
    output to crusher east side
    forget

    -- ========================================================================
    -- CÃ‚MARA DE PURIFICAÃ‡ÃƒO
    -- ========================================================================
    -- Purifica minerais para maior rendimento
    
    input from input_pc
    output to purification_chamber east side
    forget

    -- ========================================================================
    -- COMPRESSOR DE Ã“SMIO
    -- ========================================================================
    -- Comprime Ã³smio em lingotes
    
    input from input_oc
    output to osmium_compressor east side
    forget

    -- ========================================================================
    -- INFUSOR QUÃMICO (DESABILITADO)
    -- ========================================================================
    -- Combina gases para criar novos compostos quÃ­micos
    -- Atualmente comentado - descomente se necessÃ¡rio
    
    --input from input_cif
    --output to chemical_infuser east side

    -- ========================================================================
    -- INJETORES QUÃMICOS
    -- ========================================================================
    -- Injeta gases especÃ­ficos nos materiais para processamento avanÃ§ado
    
    -- Injetor de OxigÃªnio
    input from input_ci_oxygen
    output to chemical_injector_oxygen east side
    forget

    -- Injetor de Cloreto de HidrogÃªnio
    input from input_ci_hydrogen_chloride
    output to chemical_injector_hydrogen_chloride east side
    forget
    
    -- Injetor de Vapor
    input from input_ci_steam
    output to chemical_injector_steam east side
    forget
    
    -- ========================================================================
    -- SEPARADORES ELETROLÃTICOS
    -- ========================================================================
    -- Separam lÃ­quidos em seus componentes gasosos
    
    -- Separador de Ãgua (produz HidrogÃªnio e OxigÃªnio)
    input fluid::water from sink top side
    output fluid::water to ES_Water top side
    forget 

    -- Separador de Salmoura (produz Cloro e SÃ³dio)
    input fluid::brine from Brine_tank top side
    output fluid::brine to ES_Brine east side
    forget 

    -- Separador de Ãgua Pesada (produz DeutÃ©rio e OxigÃªnio)
    input fluid::heavy_water from HeavyWater_tank top side
    output fluid::heavy_water to ES_HeavyWater east side
    forget

    -- ========================================================================
    -- TORRES DE EVAPORAÃ‡ÃƒO TÃ‰RMICA
    -- ========================================================================
    -- Concentram lÃ­quidos atravÃ©s de evaporaÃ§Ã£o
    
    -- Torre de Salmoura (concentra salmoura)
    input fluid::brine from Brine_tank bottom side
    output fluid::brine to thermal_evaporation_tower_brine east side
    forget

    -- Torre de Ãgua (produz vapor)
    input fluid::water from sink top side
    output fluid::water to thermal_evaporation_tower_water west side
    forget

    -- ========================================================================
    -- COLETA DE GASES DOS SEPARADORES
    -- ========================================================================
    -- Transfere gases produzidos para tanques de armazenamento especÃ­ficos
    
    -- Coleta Cloro do Separador de Salmoura (saÃ­da norte)
    input from ES_Brine north side
    output to chlorine_tank top side
    forget

    -- Coleta SÃ³dio do Separador de Salmoura (saÃ­da sul)
    input from ES_Brine south side
    output to sodium_tank top side
    forget

    -- Coleta DeutÃ©rio do Separador de Ãgua Pesada (saÃ­da norte)
    input from ES_HeavyWater north side
    output to deuterium_tank top side
    forget

    -- Coleta OxigÃªnio do Separador de Ãgua Pesada (saÃ­da sul)
    input from ES_HeavyWater south side
    output to oxygen_tank top side
    forget

end

-- FIM DO SCRIPT DE AUTOMAÃ‡ÃƒO MEKANISM

title: MC 1.12.2 Turtle Programm: FlÃ¤chenbau (nicht fertig)
content:
local Version = 0.1
local Header = "---------------------------------------\n              FlÃ¤chenbau V"..Version.."          \n---------------------------------------"
 
function clear()
    shell.run("clear")
    print(""..Header.."")
end
local drehen = "L"
local level = 0
local block = 0
local sel = 1
local wait = 0.5
--local hoch = 0
clear()
 
--======================================================================================================================================
 
function Beginn()
    --durchgaenge = hoch
	turtle.select(sel)
    drehungen = breit
    for b = 0, breit - 1 do
        Durchgang()
        drehungen = drehungen - 1
        if drehungen > 0 then
            Drehen()
        end
    end
    Zurueck()
    clear()
    --Steigen()
    --[[
    print("Soll ich weiter hoch?\nBin aktuell "..level.." ebenen hoch gegangen.")
    weiter2 = io.read()
    if weiter2 == "ja" then
        level = level + 1
        Steigen()
    end
    if weiter2 == "nein" then
        clear()
        print("Ok dann gehe ich auf ausgangsposition zurÃ¼ck\nund starte dann neu.")
        Senken()
        --sleep(2)
        --shell.run("clear")
    end
    ]]
end
 
function Senken()
    while level > 0 do
        turtle.down()
        level = level - 1
        print(""..level.."")
    end
end
 
function Steigen()
    print("level: "..level.."\nhoch: "..hoch.."")
    if hoch > 0 then
        level = level + 1
        hoch = hoch - 1
        print("level: "..level.."\nhoch: "..hoch.."")
    end
    --[[
    if hoch >= "0" then
        print("Steigen")
        while turtle.detectUp() do
            turtle.digUp()
            sleep(1)
        end
        turtle.up()
        hoch = hoch - 1
        level = level + 1
        Beginn()
    end
    if hoch >= 0 then
        print("Senken")
        Senken()
    end
    ]]
end
 
function Zurueck()
	while not turtle.detectDown() do
        turtle.placeDown()
		block = block+1
		blockCheck()
        sleep(wait)
    end
    if drehen == "R" then
        turtle.turnRight()
        for b = 1, breit - 1 do
            turtle.back()
        end
        turtle.turnRight()
    else
        for l = 1, lang - 1 do
            turtle.back()
        end
        turtle.turnLeft()
        for b = 1, breit - 1 do
            turtle.back()
        end
        turtle.turnRight()
    end
	shell.run("reboot")
    --frage()
end
 
function frage()
    print("MÃ¶chtest du das ich eine weitere ebene abbaue?\nJa oder Nein")
    oben = io.read()
    if oben == "ja" then
        while turtle.detectUp() do
            turtle.digUp()
            sleep(wait)
        end
        turtle.up()
        Beginn()
    else
        shell.run("reboot")
     end
end
 
function Durchgang()
    for l = 1, lang - 1 do
		while not turtle.detectDown() do
			turtle.placeDown()
			block = block+1
			blockCheck()
			sleep(wait)
		end
        --[[while turtle.detect() do
            turtle.dig()
            sleep(1)
        end]]
        turtle.forward()
    end
end
 
function Drehen()
    if drehen == "L" then
        turtle.turnLeft()
        while not turtle.detectDown() do
			turtle.placeDown()
			block = block+1
			blockCheck()
			sleep(wait)
		end
        turtle.forward()
        turtle.turnLeft()
        drehen = "R"
    else
        turtle.turnRight()
        while not turtle.detectDown() do
			turtle.placeDown()
			block = block+1
			blockCheck()
			sleep(wait)
		end
        turtle.forward()
        turtle.turnRight()
        drehen = "L"
    end
end

function blockCheck()
	if block == 64 then
		sel = sel+1
		turtle.select(sel)
		block = 0
	end
end

function placeDown()
	while not turtle.detectDown() do
        turtle.placeDown()
		block = block+1
		blockCheck()
        sleep(wait)
    end
end
--======================================================================================================================================
 
--print("Wie hoch soll der Bereich werden? (nicht verfÃ¼gbar)")
local hoch = "1"
--clear()
print("Wie lang soll der Bereich werden?")
print("Bedenke maximale FlÃ¤che 32x32!\n")
lang = io.read()
clear()
print("Wie breit soll der Bereich werden?")
print("Bedenke maximale FlÃ¤che 32x32!\n")
breit = io.read()
clear()
print("Bedenke das ich in der unteren rechten Ecke des Raumes stehen muss um zu starten.\n")
print("Bedenke maximale FlÃ¤che 32x32!\n")
print("\nWenn ich dort stehe schreibe; ok")
weiter1 = io.read()
clear()
if weiter1 == "Ok" or "ok" or "OK" then
    Beginn()
end

title: refueling miner
content:
-- chunkminer.lua
-- Mines a 16x16 chunk, auto-refuels from a chest behind it

-- === CONFIG ===
local LENGTH = 16
local WIDTH = 16

-- === STATE ===
local x, y, z = 0, 0, 0 -- Position tracking
local dir = 0 -- 0=north,1=east,2=south,3=west
local layer = 0

-- === HELPERS ===
local function turnLeft() turtle.turnLeft(); dir = (dir + 3) % 4 end
local function turnRight() turtle.turnRight(); dir = (dir + 1) % 4 end

local function forward()
    while not turtle.forward() do
        turtle.dig()
        turtle.attack()
        sleep(0.4)
    end
    if dir == 0 then z = z - 1
    elseif dir == 1 then x = x + 1
    elseif dir == 2 then z = z + 1
    elseif dir == 3 then x = x - 1 end
end

local function up()
    while not turtle.up() do
        turtle.digUp()
        turtle.attackUp()
        sleep(0.4)
    end
    y = y + 1
end

local function down()
    while not turtle.down() do
        turtle.digDown()
        turtle.attackDown()
        sleep(0.4)
    end
    y = y - 1
end

-- === REFUELING ===
local function refuel()
    if turtle.getFuelLevel() == "unlimited" then return end
    if turtle.getFuelLevel() > 100 then return end

    print("Refueling...")
    local turned = false

    -- Turn around to face the chest
    turnLeft()
    turnLeft()
    turned = true

    -- Try to suck fuel from chest
    for slot = 1, 16 do
        local detail = turtle.getItemDetail(slot)
        if detail == nil then
            turtle.suck()
            detail = turtle.getItemDetail(slot)
        end
        if detail and turtle.refuel(1) then
            while turtle.refuel(1) do end
        end
    end

    if turned then
        turnLeft()
        turnLeft()
    end

    print("Fuel Level: " .. turtle.getFuelLevel())
end

-- === MINING ===
local function mineLayer()
    for row = 1, WIDTH do
        for col = 1, LENGTH - 1 do
            refuel()
            turtle.digDown()
            turtle.dig()
            forward()
        end
        if row < WIDTH then
            if row % 2 == 1 then
                turnRight()
                turtle.dig()
                forward()
                turnRight()
            else
                turnLeft()
                turtle.dig()
                forward()
                turnLeft()
            end
        end
    end

    -- Return to start of this layer
    if WIDTH % 2 == 1 then
        turnRight()
    else
        turnLeft()
    end
    for i = 1, WIDTH - 1 do
        forward()
    end
    if WIDTH % 2 == 1 then
        turnRight()
    else
        turnLeft()
    end
    for i = 1, LENGTH - 1 do
        forward()
    end
end

-- === MAIN ===
local function main()
    print("Starting 16x16 chunk mining...")
    refuel()

    -- Go down until solid
    while not turtle.detectDown() do
        down()
    end

    -- Mine layers upward until ceiling hit or full inventory
    while true do
        mineLayer()
        print("Layer complete. Going up...")
        up()

        if turtle.detectUp() then
            print("Ceiling reached, stopping.")
            break
        end
    end

    print("Chunk mining complete!")
end

main()
